data.text:
13.6.24 with EB.Â Definitely not my choice of date!Â Â

After spending entirely too much time photographing Lego, did a very quick wander through the rest of the place.Â "The Drop" is still there, but none of the other "circus" stuff from 20 years ago is.Â The Tesla Coil, tornado, big Jupiter cloud spinny ball thing and earthquake machine are all still there (although the latter was out for repairs).

Ferro fluid

The Gravatram has been moved into the museum, but wasn't working

Tesla coil

Tornado

Thermal camera.Â I'd love to own one of these!

The last time I was there was 2007 and before that 2003.Â Need to go again and allocate more time.Â And not during school holidays!!
